Class TimeSortByAvgDesireComparator

java.lang.Object
  scheduler.generate.TimeSortByAvgDesireComparator
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.Comparator
public class TimeSortByAvgDesireComparator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Comparator

Compares two strings of the form: [number]_[Hour of day]:[Minute of day]. The "number" part of the String will determine the order of itmes. In the event of a tie, a Time object will be constructed, and the earlier Time will be given precedence over a later one.
